{"word":"H4694 - מְצוּרָה - mᵉtsûwrâh - mets-oo-raw' - Fenced","slug":"H4694","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מְצוּרָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mᵉtsûwrâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mets-oo-raw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Fenced"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E6;&#x05E8;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05E6;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05E8;&#x05D4; - m<sup>e</sup>tsu&#x0302;ra&#x0302;h  m<sup>e</sup>tsu&#x0302;ra&#x0302;h</b> - <i>mets-oo-raw', mets-oo-raw'</i><p/>Feminine of <a href=\"#/H4692\">H4692</a>; a <i>hemming</i> in, that is, (objectively) a <i>mound</i> (of siege), or (subjectively) a <i>rampart</i> (of protection), (abstractly) <i>fortification: - </i>fenced (city,) fort, munition, strong hold."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4692\">H4692</a>, <a href=\"#/H6696\">H6696</a>, <a href=\"#/H6887\">H6887</a>"}]}